<!-- ====================================================================== 
   El calentamiento es un <exploration> (distinto a las otras actividades)
   Para RRRRR usar el estilo del calentamiento. Por ejemplo, usar 
   RRRRRR=observa con los "Observa y Pregúntate"
===========================================================================  -->
<exploration xml:id="warm-converNum-cualesNumEnteros" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>16: It’s 16 parts of 1, which is 16.</li>
      <li>8: I know 2 halves make 1, so I count by 2 halves like 2 halves, 4 halves, and so on, to get to 16 halves, and I counted 8 times.</li>
      <li>4: There are 4 fourths in 1, so 8 fourths in 2, and 16 fourths in 4.</li>
      <li>5: If <m>\frac{16}{4}</m> is 4, then 4 more fourths would make 5.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


